04. POST /entities on CB of an entity urn:E1 with attr P1,P3,P6 (matching R1-3), and one attribute 'A1' to stay in CB
=====================================================================================================================
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Length: 0
Date: REGEX(.*)
Location: /ngsi-ld/v1/entities/urn:E1



